# Supabase (optional) — enables accounts + saving up to 5 teams.
# Create a free project at https://supabase.com, then copy these from
# Project Settings → API. Both are PUBLIC/client-safe (row-level security
# protects the data). Never put the service_role key here.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values, then rebuild.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR-ANON-PUBLIC-KEY
